snippet.title: Slendrina Must Die: The School
snippet.description:
Help Poison Games work more efficiently, check this link https://gogetfunding.com/one-cup-of-coffee-so-i-can-work-more-easily/ Thanks

Play Online: https://www.crazygames.com/game/slendrina-must-die-the-school
Android Download: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.PoisonGames.SlendrinaMustDieTheSchool
PC Download: https://gamejolt.com/games/slendrina_must_die_the-school/395157

Find 8 fuses that are scattered throughout the school.
Those fuses will open a door, a classroom door, special classroom for a special student!

p.s. you must find her teddy bear to get something in return.

Features:

* Four weapons: 
- Knife
- Gun
- Shotgun
- DeathSword for melee attack

* Awesome 3D Graphics
* Smooth Controls.
* High quality 3D environment graphics.
* Gameplay from Poison Games that you love.
* Big Map with lots of Horror and Action.
